  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Content"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title",
      "label": "Title",
      "default": "Why Choose GODSPEED?"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "content",
      "label": "Content",
      "default": "<p>We offer the most beautiful and stylish e-bikes on the market. They're not just for hobbies or weekends – our bikes are designed for daily use in all conditions. Comfortable, elegant, and equipped with accessories like fenders and baskets, they're perfect for anyone who wants to travel sustainably and stylishly.</p><p>GODSPEED is Ticino's first e-bike shop specializing in everyday transportation: city bikes, cargo bikes for transport, and a selection of e-MTBs for adventure seekers. Perfect for commuters, parents, and sports enthusiasts – our bikes are for everyone seeking an alternative means of transport.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Image"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "image",
      "label": "Image"
    },
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "image_position",
      "label": "Image Position",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "left",
          "label": "Left"
